OL,6,FUnions have accused a Government
OL,7,Fminister of "avoiding" engagement with
OL,8,Fworkers during recent visits to steel
OL,9,Fplants.
OL,11,FIndustry minister Alan Mak travelled
OL,12,Fto four sites, including , where as
OL,13,Fowner Tata moves to produce steel in a
OL,14,Fmore environmentally friendly way.
OL,16,FMr Mak spent three hours in Port
OL,17,FTalbot and also visited Celsa Steel in
OL,18,FCardiff and British Steel plants in
OL,19,Fthe North East.
