OL,6,FHe said in a statement that the
OL,7,FGovernment is backing the UK steel
OL,8,Findustry for the long term.
OL,10,FHe was given a tour of the site of the
OL,11,Fproposed new electric arc furnace in
OL,12,FPort Talbot, which will replace
OL,13,Fexisting coal-powered blast furnaces.
