OL,3,CMinister accused of 'sneaking around
OL,4,Csteel site' during visit
OL,6,FAlun Davies, national officer of the
OL,7,FCommunity trade union, said: "We note
OL,8,Fthat the latest industry minister has
OL,9,Fbeen sneaking around steel sites this
OL,10,Fweek whilst avoiding any engagement
OL,11,Fwith steelworkers. Perhaps that's
OL,12,Funderstandable, as our members would
OL,13,Fhave told him what they think of his
OL,14,FGovernment's approach to steel.
OL,16,F"We've had a long succession of steel
OL,17,Fministers under the Conservatives:
OL,18,Fwe're now on our 13th since 2010.
OL,19,FThat's resulted in a woeful lack of
OL,20,Fleadership and direction for the
OL,21,Findustry in tumultuous times.
