OL,3,CMinister accused of 'sneaking around
OL,4,Csteel site' during visit
OL,6,F"Amidst the ministerial merry-go-round
OL,7,Fthere's been one constant feature ` a
OL,8,FGovernment which sees steel as a
OL,9,Fproblem to get off its desk, rather
OL,10,Fthan the base for an advanced
OL,11,Findustrial strategy for the future.
OL,13,F"The minister had the audacity to
OL,14,Ftrumpet the Government's deal with
OL,15,FTata during his whistle-stop visit to
OL,16,FPort Talbot this week.
