OL,3,CMinister accused of 'sneaking around
OL,4,Csteel site' during visit
OL,6,F"This bargain-basement deal will leave
OL,7,Fthe UK as an outlier in the G20 as the
OL,8,Fonly country unable to make its own
OL,9,Fprimary steel. It will mean exporting
OL,10,Fjobs and importing dirty steel, with a
OL,11,Fdevastating impact on the local
OL,12,Fcommunity. No wonder the minister
OL,13,Fdidn't want to stick around to hear
OL,14,Fthe truth."
