OL,3,CMinister accused of 'sneaking around
OL,4,Csteel site' during visit
OL,6,FMr Mak said: "This Government is
OL,7,Fbacking the UK steel industry for the
OL,8,Flong term, and I'm pleased my first
OL,9,Fvisit as industry minister is to see
OL,10,Fthe steelmaking operation up close and
OL,11,Fshow our commitment to the sector is
OL,12,Fstronger than ever, building on recent
OL,13,Fwins for UK steel including the launch
OL,14,Fof our British Industry Supercharger,
OL,15,Fwhich will cut costs and give a huge
OL,16,Fboost to businesses."
OL,18,FTata insists its plans for Port Talbot
OL,19,Fwill secure the plant's future and
OL,20,Favoid even heavier job losses.
